{"tid":2188080,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「蘇9」致電基亞連尼：唔好介意咬過你","createTime":"2020-09-04T04:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T05:29:23.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f69e3019afe6e3cc30170cb4b715f1bcafab7470","tid":2188080,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:34:25.000Z","msg":"巴塞球星蘇亞雷斯（Luis Suarez）給祖記後衛基亞連尼（Giorgio Chiellini）打了電話，就當年的「咬人事件」進行和解。<br />\n<br />\n  在2014年巴西世界盃烏拉圭與意大利的比賽中，蘇亞雷斯咬了基亞連尼的肩膀，當時逃過了球證的處罰，不過，他在後來被追加處罰停賽四個月。<br />\n<br />\n  據《米蘭體育報》稱，如今蘇亞雷斯有望加盟祖雲達斯，他於是給祖記隊長基亞連尼打了電話，試圖化解當年風波，拉近兩人的關係。<br />\n<br />\n  其實基亞連尼在事後並未記仇，他曾在採訪中說：「這是他在近身搏鬥中的招數，我也有這類招數，他和我有點相似。」而蘇亞雷斯當年也曾承認：「我錯了，但我也是人，會有衝動的時候。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/09/04/5/57691e13ba3029e9d4fdd2081c48a86f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F09%2F04%2F5%2F57691e13ba3029e9d4fdd2081c48a86f.jpg&h=448aea0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76ed6fb08141c6eb4d892efdf743c7d6b027c956","tid":2188080,"uid":12628,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"牙蘇個電話比人勾線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e0c66c7b704f89024d46b4c247af479715f0b2","tid":2188080,"uid":99700,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:40:28.000Z","msg":"「這是他在近身搏鬥中的招數，我也有這類招數，他和我有點相似。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c6c8b5fe59b125bbfff011d319756d940c7501","tid":2188080,"uid":34457,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"兩個廣東話都講得幾好"},{"pid":"0361eebcb0741952f90017d332f4083cfc7a26f7","tid":2188080,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75215ca19299334487e54524d46bb66ee34b16a1","tid":2188080,"uid":204126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:19:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d59e7dd9a316dd921ed87f76d311c220f366f95","tid":2188080,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3c6c8b5fe59b125bbfff011d319756d940c7501","tid":2188080,"uid":34457,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"兩個廣東話都講得幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"國語黎"},{"pid":"8f71d9e20ea38e503d0b69dedfb6d2d436a89c63","tid":2188080,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"幾過癮"}]}